    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do something in Real Life for once!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real Life is a firstperson shooter set in the semi-open world of Reality. Go from planet to planet, ruining lives, stealing weapons and doing whatever the head tells you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">__________________________________________</span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>KILL everyone and take their money!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/356e9689264454b6a0194a66206f8090.avif?t=1746472325\" width=350 height=268 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Dodge attacks by using the advanced movement options provided to the Blenderman!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/03283280b8e8f6998cb0a589379c46c0.poster.avif?t=1746472325\" width=357 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/03283280b8e8f6998cb0a589379c46c0.webm?t=1746472325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Block enemy attacks and send back the damage with the parry!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/4e30b7592da7763894e15396b69f0366.poster.avif?t=1746472325\" width=356 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/4e30b7592da7763894e15396b69f0366.webm?t=1746472325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/4e30b7592da7763894e15396b69f0366.mp4?t=1746472325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Customize the Blenderman with new colors and awesome hats!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/7e3d255fb83a7fd80315865dc251dbd1.avif?t=1746472325\" width=350 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Explore strange new worlds and talk to weird aliens.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/a6cb61652e26d32614a3fad8ec9cc99e.avif?t=1746472325\" width=350 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Climactic one on one duels at the end of each board!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/5fa682b9d300c0a71594f27414be1d4c.poster.avif?t=1746472325\" width=356 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/5fa682b9d300c0a71594f27414be1d4c.webm?t=1746472325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/5fa682b9d300c0a71594f27414be1d4c.mp4?t=1746472325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">___________</span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>You cannot be stopped... You are the Blenderman!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/7fbf4c11c822d6e157b6c721311100a1.poster.avif?t=1746472325\" width=270 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756310/extras/7fbf4c11c822d6e157b6c721311100a1.webm?t=1746472325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
